<br>
Delilah's sparkling brown eyes watched all the movement in the village as the tiger stopped in the center of the village where the bonfire would usually be. She lifted her hands above her head and stretched before getting off her tiger and patting it affectionately. The tiger purred a rumbling purr as it closed it's eyes and settled down and napped for a while.<br>
<br>
Delilah stretched out her limbs and refitted her weaponry on her. She needed to become more informed on the situation at hand and began to wander around the village, having not been in here in so long. Perhaps she would find an amazon who was very well aware of the situation at hand and could ask her for assistance in anything at all. Delilah needed to see a map... a path.. something to follow to head into battle. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ukalaofsmyrna.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kala of Smyrna</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#993300>(8/19/01 4:10:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/amznkala/images/kala-01.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Kala Arrives</span><hr size=1> After what seemed forever,Kala finally arrived in the lands of Scynthia.She didn't look so good,she had barely slept during the trip from Smyrna to Scynthia,and it was apparent from the dark circles under her eyes.<br>
<br>
She reaches the village gates,where two gaurds were now on duty.She gives the gaurds a slight nod,and as they reckognize her they allow her to enter the village.Nudging her steed onward,she enters the village,and stops as she reaches the center of it.<br>
<br>
With some difficulty she dismounts her the steed,giving herself little time to stretch,she then leads the war steed to a pole and ties it off before turning and heading back to the center of the village.<br>
<br>
Her left hand resting on her swollen stomach,she looks around at the movement of her fellow amazons.It didnt seem like many had prepared themselves for the battle,but Kala knew when the time came,they would be ready.<br>
<br>
She didn't exactly know what was going on,except Alysia's tribe was going to war with some other tribe called Saurian's.Her athelfi needed help,and thats all Kala really had to know.<br>
<br>
Waiting for more news of whats going to happen next,she walks over to a wooden bench and sits,some rest would be better than none,and so she waits. <p>|•| Kala of Smyrna |•|</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udelilahtragedy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delilah Tragedy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#993300>(8/21/01 12:00:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Saurian Wars</span><hr size=1> After Delilah's tour of the village, she figured the Queen had already left with part of her tribe. She shook her head and headed immediately for the Queen's Hut. Since she couldn't find the queen herself, she needed to see some maps so she walked through the doors of Alysia's Hut.<br>
<br>
Her shimmering brown eyes spotted the desk instantly and walked over to it and turned the map to face it in the right direction which would be in accordance to the village from her angle. She placed a solitary index finger on the map and then removed it and the map began to move according to the wind of the lands and any movements in fields and clearings and even movements in this village and in the Saurian community. The map was large enough so each person could be represented by the most minte dots. This made the map look more like i was covered by ants but it still worked.<br>
<br>
She bent down and inspected the now skittering details of the map. Wow.. the Saurian people were quite a community. She scrunched up her nose as she watched small formations of dots in the Saurian side and the scattering of Amazons. Oh this will not work too well. Del needed to get out there as fast as she could. She rolled up the animated map and shoved it in her belt and took off out of the Queen's Hut and went to the center of the village where her tiger was already ready having sensed Del's urgency. She mounted her tiger and off they went back into the forest heading for war. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Evelyn Saphros</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/21/01 10:40:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=178.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Miracle?</span><hr size=1> Somehow,a miracle perhaps,the young Evelyn managed to make it to Scynthia upon her quite large dog,Scooby.Yep,she followed some of the other amazons here,it wasnt out of character for her,she often did stupid things in this kind of nature.<br>
<br>
&quot;Woah Scooby,Woah.&quot;She pleads with her dog to stop,until he finally does,skidding to a stop so fast,Evelyn looses her grip and flies over Scoobys head,and lands on her stomach,but not before doing a few tumbles.&quot;Owwwch!&quot;She had skid her knee in the fall,and dropped her wooden sword,with a sniffle and a few tears running down her cheeks,she gets to her feet,and looks at Scooby.&quot;Stupid dog!&quot;She sniffles once more,and wripes her eyes,then bends down and picks up her wooden sword.&quot;You didnt hava stop so fast.&quot;Scooby mearly tilts his head,his ears perking slightly.&quot;Come on,we gotsa find the amazons.&quot;And with that she runs around until she spots some amazons dressed in thier war gear,and quickly Evelyn ducks behind a water barrel,and looks at Scooby.&quot;Hide.&quot;She whispers,and Scooby just prances around.Evelyn sighs and watches the amazons as they head off to join the others in battle.<br>
